@startuml
title Client DB Surface (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontColor #111111
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "SDK Consumer" as Consumer #D6EAF8
component "createClient(...)" as Client #D5F5E3
component "Root methods\nfrom / rpc / query" as RootApi #FCF3CF
component "TableQueryBuilder" as TableBuilder #FADBD8
component "Gateway HTTP Client" as Gateway #E8DAEF

Consumer --> Client : build client
Client --> RootApi : expose db operations at root
Consumer --> RootApi : call from(...)/rpc(...)/query(...)
RootApi --> TableBuilder : from(table)
TableBuilder --> Gateway : execute fetch/insert/update/delete/query/rpc
RootApi --> Gateway : query/rpc direct

note right of RootApi
No dedicated db namespace.
Module expansion point is limited.
end note
@enduml
